OK F-70-D-9 STREAMS FISHERIES MANAGEMENT GRANT 

FUNDS ARE TO BE USED TO SUPPORT THE DEPARTMENT'S STREAMS FISHERIES MANAGEMENT REGION IN (1) LOGISTIC SUPPORT, ADMINISTRATION, AND OPERATIONS; 
(2) ASSESSMENT OF SPORT FISH POPULATIONS; AND (3)TECHNICAL ASSISTANCE TO PUBLIC, PRIVATE, AND ORGANIZATIONAL ENTITIES.

PR-F-F19AF01251 LUCHETTI RESERVOIR AND YAUCO URBAN PARK (F-29-27) - TO CONTINUE THE MANAGEMENT AND ACCESS OF SPORT FISHING AND BOATING ACTIVITIES; 
MAINTAIN THE FACILITIES AND ACQUIRED EQUIPMENT; AND PROVIDE INFORMATION AND RECRUIT NEW ANGLERS; AND OBTAIN INFORMATION ON THE HEALTH 
OF THE FISH POPULATIONS, ANGLERS' EFFORTS AND SATISFACTION.
